subject: Re: Some new files from the 12-469 Old Style RS Box

No, not really.  If i had to take a guess, i would say it is the fact 
that other spirit entities sometimes can't get past the grounded ones 
in my home.  The grounded spirits seem to be more dominant and block 
the others out at times coming through the box.  That always bugged 
me because the grounded spirits only block others, they never speak 
with me.  I would like to find out who is here and why, but they 
never answer me.

-Steve H.
